‼ Welcoming a new Alumni Ambassador, Callie ‼

At her home campus of Arcadia University, Callie studies psychology and sports management, and is part Team Impact and the Honors Program. She is also a NCAA student athlete on the women's field hockey team 🏑

During her semester abroad, Callie exchanged Pennsylvania for beautiful beach-side Australia, studying at the University of Wollongong! She quickly grew to love the slower lifestyle, proximity to the ocean, and wild koalas throughout the city 🐨

As one of our Alumni Ambassadors, Callie is happy to chat with you about her time in Wollongong! Please send her a message at cfalzone@arcadia.edu!

